backport

1) git clone ssh://josferna@code.engineering.redhat.com:22/rhs-glusterfs
2) git checkout -b <branch name u fancy> -t origin/rhgs-3.1.2
3) cherry pick the master patch which u want to backport
4) git commit -as --amend
5) Edit the commit message
6) Clone the master bug and select redhat product
component dht
7) ./rfc
give the new bug id


